  "action_title": "Change mowing regime (e.g. timing, frequency, height)",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nWe found no studies that evaluated the effects of changing mowing regime (e.g. timing, frequency, height) on mammals.\n\n\u2018We found no studies'\u2019 means that we have not yet found any studies that have directly evaluated this intervention during our systematic journal and report searches. Therefore, we have no evidence to indicate whether or not the intervention has any desirable or harmful effects."
}

